SHELL variable
set:
VAR_NAME=VALUE    //can be: 100, "fsd", /dev/sda1

get:
echo $VAR_NAME

unset:
unset VARIABLE_NAME



ENVIRONMENT variable
set:
export VAR_NAME=VALUE

get:
echo $VAR_NAME
printenv VAR_NAME

unset:
unset VARIABLE_NAME


ADD FOREVER:
add "export VAR_NAME=VALUE" line to: ~/.bash_profile